        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Efficient Public Buildings Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to provide grants to states, local governments, or nonprofit organizations for making energy improvements in (1) public libraries, (2) public hospitals, (3) community centers, or (4) state or local government buildings.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
